Explorer's rings are rewards from the Lumbridge & Draynor Diary obtained by speaking to Hatius Cosaintus in Lumbridge. The different upgrades of Explorer's rings are:

  • Explorer's ring 1, from the easy tasks set
  • Explorer's ring 2, from the medium tasks set
  • Explorer's ring 3, from the hard tasks set
  • Explorer's ring 4, from the elite tasks set

'''Explorer's rings''' are rewards from the [[Lumbridge & Draynor Diary]] obtained by speaking to [[Hatius Cosaintus]] in [[Lumbridge]]. The different upgrades of Explorer's rings are:

*[[Explorer's ring 1]], from the easy tasks set
*[[Explorer's ring 2]], from the medium tasks set
*[[Explorer's ring 3]], from the hard tasks set
*[[Explorer's ring 4]], from the elite tasks set
